  David Golden <dagolden@cpan.org>
  
  =item *
  
  Ricardo Signes <rjbs@cpan.org>
  
  =back
  
  =head1 CONTRIBUTORS
  
  =for stopwords Ed J Karen Etheridge Leon Timmermans robario
  
  =over 4
  
